 "lrc": "[00:02.48]Yeah\n[00:04.40]one tap away\n[00:08.40]but somehow everybody far now\n[00:13.44]uh\n[00:14.64]check it\n[00:15.28]Back-back when the screen made the room glow\n[00:18.08]I thought the whole world would move close\n[00:20.40]old names popping up like whoa though\n[00:23.36]middle school faces in a new post\n[00:24.96]I thought we’d talk-talk, really get honest\n[00:27.92]drop the mask, no fake persona\n[00:30.16]find your tribe, find your people\n[00:32.80]make the whole cold world feel warmer\n[00:35.44]Ads in the cracks, brands in the chat\n[00:37.76]everybody got stats, everybody wants claps\n[00:40.24]everybody got reach but don’t reach back\n[00:42.80]how we got this close and lost contact?\n[00:45.28]You can see me in a second\n[00:47.84]You can call me any day\n[00:50.40]You can love me in private\n[00:52.32]But scroll right past my name\n[00:55.36]Funny how we got connected\n[00:57.44]Then forgot how to stay\n[01:00.48]You're right there in my pocket\n[01:02.16]But you feel a world away\n[01:03.68]One tap away (one tap away)\n[01:08.88]From a real conversation but we don't say a thing\n[01:11.52]We're one tap away\n[01:13.84]From \"I see you keep going\" from \"I'm proud of your dream\"\n[01:16.72]Save your likes for the strangers\n[01:18.24]Save your hearts for the stars\n[01:21.60]But the ones who really know you act like loving you is hard\n[01:26.16]One tap away\n[01:27.68]So why do I feel alone in a room full of names?\n[01:31.84]Tap, tap, but you don't reach back\n[01:34.32]Heart, heart, but it don't feel like that\n[01:36.96]Close, close, close, but we don't connect\n[01:39.20]One tap away and we still forget\n[01:42.00]Click, click, click, everybody got a new rule\n[01:44.80]Don't hype friends that ain't cool, cool\n[01:47.60]Save that love for the big names\n[01:49.52]Blue checks, big chains, big views\n[01:52.00]Then if a stranger blow up overnight\n[01:54.72]Everybody swear they saw the light\n[01:56.48]Same ones quiet when you need a fire\n[01:59.28]Now they in the comments like \"that's my guy\"\n[02:01.92]We one tap away\n[02:04.48]one tap away\n[02:05.44]from a real conversation\n[02:09.76]but we don’t say a thing\n[02:12.64]Save your likes for the strangers\n[02:24.40]save your hearts for the stars\n[02:27.68]but the ones who really know you\n[02:29.92]act like loving you is hard\n[02:32.48]Maybe I was young\n[02:33.44]thinking wires could heal us\n[02:34.96]thinking all this light\n[02:36.00]would finally reveal us\n[02:37.44]I’m not hard to find\n[02:38.88]I’m not far away\n[02:39.76]I’m still right here\n[02:42.40]one tap away\n[02:44.51]We one tap away\n[02:51.68]one tap away\n[02:51.84]so why do I feel alone\n[02:51.84]in a room full of names?\n[02:53.76]one tap away\n[02:54.96]and still so far\n[02:56.32]everybody online\n[02:59.52]nobody where you are\n"
